INSERT INTO `recipe` VALUES (1,'Spaghetti','Spaghetti, a quintessential Italian dish, is a comforting and satisfying meal known for its simplicity and versatility. Thin strands of pasta are cooked to al dente perfection and generously coated in a savory tomato-based sauce. The sauce, often infused with garlic, onions, and herbs, creates a flavorful and aromatic combination. Variations can include additions like meatballs, grated Parmesan cheese, or fresh basil, enhancing the overall taste experience. This classic pasta dish is a timeless favorite, offering a delightful blend of textures and flavors.',15,30,'imgs/recipes/r6.jpeg','Dinner','Italian','Gluten-Free','Boiled','Pasta','Intermediate',4),(2,'Vegetarian Stir-Fry','A Vegetarian Stir-Fry is a vibrant and healthful dish that celebrates the crispiness of fresh vegetables combined with the umami of soy sauce and the warmth of ginger and garlic. Colorful bell peppers, broccoli, carrots, and other veggies are quickly stir-fried in a wok, maintaining their bright colors and crunchy texture. The dish is not only visually appealing but also a nutritional powerhouse. Served over a bed of rice or noodles, this stir-fry is a quick and delicious way to enjoy a variety of vegetables in one flavorful ensemble.',10,15,'imgs/recipes/r20.jpeg','Main','Asian','Low-Carb','Stir-fry','Vegetables','Easy',1),(3,'Chicken Alfredo','Chicken Alfredo is a decadent pasta dish that marries the creamy richness of Alfredo sauce with succulent grilled chicken. Fettuccine noodles are bathed in a luscious sauce made from butter, heavy cream, and Parmesan cheese. The grilled chicken, seasoned to perfection, adds a savory and protein-packed element to the dish. The result is a harmonious blend of textures and flavors, making Chicken Alfredo a favorite among those seeking comfort in a bowl of pasta.',25,25,'imgs/recipes/r19.jpeg','Breakfast','Italian','Dairy-Free','Sauteed','Chicken','Intermediate',5),(4,'Quinoa Salad','Quinoa Salad is a wholesome and nutritious dish that highlights the versatility of quinoa, a protein-packed grain. Cooked quinoa serves as the base for this salad, mingling with a colorful assortment of fresh vegetables such as cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, and bell peppers. The salad is often dressed in a zesty vinaigrette, enhancing the flavors and providing a light and refreshing quality. Packed with vitamins and minerals, Quinoa Salad is a delightful option for those seeking a satisfying and health-conscious meal.',15,15,'imgs/recipes/r1.jpeg','Lunch','Chinese','Vegetarian','Raw','Quinoa','Easy',2),(5,'Beef Tacos','Beef Tacos, a beloved Mexican street food, offer a symphony of flavors and textures. Seasoned and grilled beef is nestled into soft corn or flour tortillas, creating a perfect vessel for an array of toppings. Common garnishes include crisp lettuce, diced tomatoes, shredded cheese, salsa, and creamy guacamole. The combination of savory, spicy, and fresh elements makes each bite a fiesta for the taste buds. Whether enjoyed as a handheld delight or plated as a taco bar, Beef Tacos provide a customizable and festive dining experience.',15,20,'imgs/recipes/r7.jpeg','Dinner','Mexican','Nut-Free','Sautéed','Beef','Intermediate',1),(6,'Vegetable Soup','Vegetable Soup is a soul-warming concoction that brings together an assortment of fresh vegetables, aromatic herbs, and a savory broth. This hearty and wholesome soup often features ingredients like carrots, celery, onions, and potatoes, creating a symphony of flavors and textures. The slow simmering allows the vegetables to release their natural sweetness, resulting in a comforting and nourishing bowl of goodness. Whether enjoyed as a starter or a complete meal, Vegetable Soup is a timeless classic that satisfies the senses and provides a comforting ',25,30,'imgs/recipes/r17.jpeg','Breakfast','Indian','Vegan','Simmered','Vegetables','Intermediate',5),(7,'Salmon Teriyaki','Salmon Teriyaki is an exquisite dish that showcases the succulence of grilled or broiled salmon glazed with a luscious teriyaki sauce. The teriyaki sauce, a blend of soy sauce, mirin, and sugar, imparts a perfect balance of sweet and savory notes to the tender salmon fillets. The result is a dish that not only delights the taste buds with its rich flavors but also captivates the eyes with its glistening, caramelized exterior. Served with a side of steamed rice and perhaps some stir-fried vegetables, Salmon Teriyaki is a culinary masterpiece that elevates the dining experience.',10,15,'imgs/recipes/r14.webp','Dinner','Japanese','Low-Carb','Grilled','Fish','Easy',1),(10,'Grilled Pork','Grilled Pork is a savory and succulent dish that celebrates the rich flavors of pork chops seasoned and grilled to perfection. The marinade, whether sweet and tangy or herb-infused, enhances the natural taste of the pork while creating a delightful caramelized exterior. The result is juicy and flavorful pork chops that make for a satisfying main course. Grilled Pork pairs well with a variety of side dishes, making it a versatile option for any occasion.',25,30,'imgs/recipes/r5.jpeg','Breakfast','Chinese','Dairy-Free','Baked','Pork','Intermediate',3),(11,'Korean Fried Rice','Fried Rice with chicken, vegetable, korean sause and sun-dried tomatoes.Korean Fried Rice, or \"Bokkeumbap,\" is a delightful dish that transforms leftover rice into a flavorful masterpiece. Stir-fried with a medley of vegetables, proteins like beef or shrimp, and seasoned with soy sauce and Korean spices, it delivers a unique and satisfying taste that showcases the essence of Korean cuisine.',15,20,'imgs/recipes/r22.jpeg','Main','Italian','Nut-Free','Boiled','Pasta','Easy',4),(12,'Beef Burger','A Beef Burger is an American classic, featuring a juicy beef patty, often seasoned with herbs and spices, grilled to perfection, and sandwiched between a soft bun. Toppings like lettuce, tomato, cheese, and condiments add layers of flavor, creating a handheld feast loved worldwide.',25,40,'imgs/recipes/r18.jpeg','Breakfast','American','Vegan','Simmered','Beans','Intermediate',1),(13,'Shrimp Scampi','Shrimp Scampi is an elegant seafood dish that stars succulent shrimp cooked in a luscious garlic and butter sauce. The dish is typically seasoned with white wine, lemon juice, and parsley, creating a harmonious balance of flavors. Served over pasta or with crusty bread, it\'s a delightful culinary experience.',15,20,'imgs/recipes/r21.jpeg','Dinner','Italian','Low-Carb','Sauteed','Shrimp','Intermediate',5),(14,'Pork Fried Rice','Pork Fried Rice is a classic Asian dish that combines fluffy rice with diced pork, vegetables, and soy sauce. Stir-fried to perfection, this dish offers a medley of textures and flavors, making it a beloved choice for those craving a delicious and satisfying meal.',15,15,'imgs/recipes/r8.jpeg','Dinner','Asian','Low-Carb','Sautéed','Vegetables','Easy',3),(15,'Strawberry Dessert','Strawberry Dessert is a sweet indulgence that showcases the natural sweetness of fresh strawberries. Whether featured in a luscious strawberry shortcake, creamy strawberry cheesecake, or as part of a fruit salad, this dessert highlights the vibrant and delightful taste of strawberries.',10,30,'imgs/recipes/r2.jpeg','Dessert','Chinese','Vegetarian','None','Berries','Easy',1),(16,'Vegetable Pizza','Vegetable Pizza is a culinary masterpiece that transforms the classic pizza into a vibrant and nutritious delight. The canvas of this pizza is typically a thin or thick crust, perfectly baked to achieve a golden-brown crispness. What makes Vegetable Pizza stand out is its colorful array of fresh and wholesome toppings. A medley of bell peppers, tomatoes, red onions, mushrooms, and other favorite vegetables are generously scattered over a base of tomato sauce. The vegetables not only add a burst of colors but also contribute a variety of textures and flavors.',30,15,'imgs/recipes/r10.jpeg','Dinner','Italian','Vegetarian','Baked','Vegetables','Intermediate',2),(17,'Turkey Wrap','Thanksgiving-inspired wrap with turkey, cranberry sauce, and stuffing.A Turkey Wrap is a wholesome and convenient meal option, featuring sliced turkey, fresh veggies, and perhaps some creamy dressing, all wrapped in a soft tortilla or flatbread. This portable delight is perfect for a quick and nutritious on-the-go lunch.',10,20,'imgs/recipes/r3.webp','Lunch','American','Dairy-Free','None','Turkey','Easy',3),(18,'Orange Soda ','Orange Soda with fresh mint leaves and blueberry base. Orange Soda is a refreshing beverage that captivates the senses with its citrusy burst. Fizzy and sweet, this effervescent drink is a popular choice for quenching thirst and providing a delightful flavor reminiscent of ripe oranges.',10,20,'imgs/recipes/r15.jpeg','Dessert','American','Low-Carb','Juice','Soda','Easy',2),(20,'Straberry Brownies','Decadent chocolate brownies, a perfect dessert treat. Strawberry Brownies offer a delightful twist on the classic chocolate treat. Fudgy brownies are studded with juicy strawberries, adding a burst of freshness to every bite. This fusion of chocolate and strawberries creates a heavenly dessert experience.',15,25,'imgs/recipes/r4.jpeg','Dessert','American','Dairy-Free','Baked','Chocolate','Easy',2),(21,'Noodle Delight','Delicious noodle dish with assorted flavors. Noodle Delight is a versatile dish that celebrates the world of noodles. Whether served in a savory broth, stir-fried with an array of veggies and proteins, or featured in a cold noodle salad, this dish invites creativity and satisfies noodle cravings in various delightful forms.',15,30,'imgs/recipes/r23.jpeg','Starter','Asian','Vegetarian','Boiling','Noodle','Intermediate',3),(22,'Crab Feast','Savory crab recipe that will leave you wanting more.A Crab Feast is a seafood extravaganza that brings people together for a delightful culinary experience. Whether enjoyed in the form of a crab boil, crab cakes, or a classic crab feast with melted butter, this indulgence highlights the sweet and succulent flavors of crab.',20,40,'imgs/recipes/r24.jpeg','Entry','Asian','Gluten-Free','Grilling','Crab','Hard',2),(23,'Prawn Paradise','A delightful prawn dish that both spicy and flavorful. Prawn Paradise is a seafood delight that features plump and juicy prawns cooked to perfection. Whether grilled, sautéed, or featured in a flavorful curry, this dish showcases the versatility of prawns and their ability to transport taste buds to a seafood paradise.',25,35,'imgs/recipes/r25.jpeg','Main','Asian','Dairy-Free','Frying','Prawn','Intermediate',1),(25,'Fish Fiesta','A feast of flavors featuring the catch of the day. A Fish Fiesta is a celebration of diverse fish dishes that span the culinary spectrum. Whether enjoyed grilled, baked, or fried, each preparation showcases the unique flavors of different fish varieties, creating a festive and flavorful dining experience.',15,25,'imgs/recipes/r27.jpeg','Entry','Korean','Low-Carb','Baking','Fish','Easy',3),(26,'Spicy Delight','A fiery and flavorful spicy fried chicken. Spicy Delight is a dish that awakens the taste buds with a fiery kick. Whether featuring spicy grilled chicken, chili-infused noodles, or a boldly seasoned curry, this dish caters to those who crave a symphony of heat and flavor.',10,20,'imgs/recipes/r28.jpeg','Starter','Asian','Dairy-Free','Grilling','Spicy Food','Intermediate',3),(28,'Bread Bonanza','Enjoy the goodness of freshly baked bread. Bread Bonanza is a celebration of artisanal bread varieties that range from crusty baguettes to soft and fluffy rolls. Whether enjoyed with savory spreads or as the foundation for creative sandwiches, this bonanza caters to bread enthusiasts.',30,40,'imgs/recipes/r30.jpeg','Main','Indian','Vegetarian','Baking','Bread','Easy',1),(30,'Fruit Bliss','Experience the taste of tropical fruits in every bite. Fruit Bliss is a dessert sensation that spotlights the delightful combination of ripe fruits. Whether featured in a fruit tart, fruit salad with honey drizzle, or as a topping for creamy desserts, this blissful creation captures the essence of sweetness from nature.',20,15,'imgs/recipes/r32.jpeg','Dessert','Thailand','Vegetarian','Blending','Fruits','Easy',4);
